&lt;p&gt;Note that,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;The series include R/4.5.3-icelake, R/4.5.3-gcc11, R/4.5.3-gcc12.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Since R_LIBS has R, R-gcc11/R-gcc12 those in their respective directories are recognised automattically.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;In the case of R/4.5.3-gcc12, a fully functional gcc/12.5.0 is made, &lt;a href=&quot;https://cambridge-ceu.github.io/csd3/systems/setup.html#fn:gcc&quot;&gt;https://cambridge-ceu.github.io/csd3/systems/setup.html#fn:gcc&lt;/a&gt;.
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;There might be some residuals from using -lintl, therefore xgboost is experimented with LIBS=”-lintl”.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;The issue goes away with gcc/12.5.0.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content><author><name>赵京华(Jing Hua Zhao)</name><email>jinghuazhao@hotmail.com</email></author><category term="info" /><summary type="html">See &amp;lt; https://cambridge-ceu.github.io/csd3/applications/R.html&amp;gt; Note that, The series include R/4.5.3-icelake, R/4.5.3-gcc11, R/4.5.3-gcc12. Since R_LIBS has R, R-gcc11/R-gcc12 those in their respective directories are recognised automattically. In the case of R/4.5.3-gcc12, a fully functional gcc/12.5.0 is made, https://cambridge-ceu.github.io/csd3/systems/setup.html#fn:gcc. There might be some residuals from using -lintl, therefore xgboost is experimented with LIBS=”-lintl”. The issue goes away with gcc/12.5.0.</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">OpenClaw 2026.3.8 is documented</title><link href="/2026/03/11/openclaw.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="OpenClaw 2026.3.8 is documented" /><published>2026-03-11T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2026-03-11T12:01:34+00:00</updated><id>/2026/03/11/openclaw</id><content type="html" xml:base="/2026/03/11/openclaw.html">&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;https://cambridge-ceu.github.io/csd3/applications/OpenClaw.html&quot;&gt;https://cambridge-ceu.github.io/csd3/applications/OpenClaw.html&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>赵京华(Jing Hua Zhao)</name><email>jinghuazhao@hotmail.com</email></author><category term="AI" /><summary type="html">See https://cambridge-ceu.github.io/csd3/applications/OpenClaw.html.</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">gaawr2 0.0.7 is published on CRAN</title><link href="/2026/03/10/gaawr2.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="gaawr2 0.0.7 is published on CRAN" /><published>2026-03-10T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2026-03-10T14:24:44+00:00</updated><id>/2026/03/10/gaawr2</id><content type="html" xml:base="/2026/03/10/gaawr2.html">&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;https://jinghuazhao.github.io/gaawr2/index.html&quot;&gt;https://jinghuazhao.github.io/gaawr2/index.html&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

